.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-OUR-RESERVE-MIN" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-our-reserve-min \- FEAT-2540 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-our-reserve-min
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-our-reserve-min for lightning CLI (FEAT-2540).
.PP
Returns the channel with the lowest our_reserve_msat.
Output: JSON from CLN with key our_reserve_msat.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
